></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div> <br/></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-9" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Pathways from overseas institutions </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-9" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>If you have completed any of the following course(s), you will be guaranteed a place in this course. In some cases, you may receive credit for your previous study, reducing the time it takes to complete your course. </p></div></div> <div class="vu-grid-container vu-card-link__grid-container vu-card-link__grid-container--grey-extra-light no-gutter-rl"><div class="vu-grid-container__inner"><div class="vu-grid-cell--12 vu-grid-cell--12@l-up vu-grid-cell--6@xl-up"><div class="vu-card-link vu-card-link__primary"><div class="no-card-link"><div class="vu-card-link__main"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-card-link__left"><div class="h5"><span class="prepend" style="display:none;"> </span>BS CIVIL ENGINEERING </div> <div class="vu-card-link-details"><span>University of Faisalabad (TUF) Pakistan, Pakistan | 192 credit points</span></div></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vu-grid-cell--12 vu-grid-cell--12@l-up vu-grid-cell--6@xl-up"><div class="vu-card-link vu-card-link__primary"><div class="no-card-link"><div class="vu-card-link__main"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-card-link__left"><div class="h5"><span class="prepend" style="display:none;"> </span>Bachelor of Civil Engineering with Honours </div> <div class="vu-card-link-details"><span>SEGI University, Malaysia, Malaysia | 192 credit points</span></div></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></div></div></div><div class