    entry_requirements = '<div class="vu-box-container__inner anchor-boxes vu-box-container__primary vu-container no-gutter-rl entry-requirements" data-id="entry-requirements" data-title="Entry requirements" id="entry-requirements"><div class="vu-container"><p style="font-weight: bold;">Entry requirements</p> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu--additional-data item-type--basic-text"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-courses--additional-data--basic-text vu-courses--additional-data--basic-text--undefined"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>Applicants for this course will need to meet the entry criteria outlined below. If you don’t meet the entry criteria, you may be able to gain entry by first completing a related course or unit(s). We call this a ‘pathway’.</p> <p> If you❛ve completed a qualification where English was the primary language of instruction, you may be eligible for an exemption of English-language requirements.</p> <p>In some cases, there may be additional entry requirements.</p> <p><a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/how-to-apply/international-applicants/entry-requirements-for-international-students" href="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/how-to-apply/international-applicants/entry-requirements-for-international-students" theme="primary"><span class="vu-link__inner"><!-- --><span>Learn more about entry requirements for international students.</span><!-- --><!-- --></span></a></p></div></div> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --></div><div class="vu--additional-data item-type--collapsible_section"><!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="collapsible-sections-container vu-courses--additional-data--collapsible_section"><div class="vu-collapsible-section"><div class="vu-collapsible-section-title" tabindex="0"><!-- --> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Entry criteria</p> <div class="vu-collapsible-toggle-icon"> <!-- --></div></div> <div class="vu-collapsible-section-content--parent" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-collapsible-section-content"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p> IELTS (or equivalent): Overall score of 5.5 with no band less than 5.0.<br/> Academic – 60% average in Australian year 11 equivalent<br></p><div class="vu-markup__table"><table align="" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse"><tbody><tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none"><span style="font-weight: bold">Country of Qualification </span></td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none"><span style="font-weight: bold">Admission Requirements </span></td></tr> <tr><td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Bangladesh</td> <td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Successful completion of Year 11 with GPA 3.0/5.0 <br>Year 12 Higher School Certificate: N/A</td></tr> <tr><td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Cambodia</td> <td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Diploma of Upper Secondary Education D average</td></tr> <tr><td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">China</td> <td style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">GAO ER (Senior Middle Year 2) 65% in academic subjects GAO SAN (Senior Middle Year 3) 60% in academic subjects </td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Indonesia</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">SMA II (grade XI) with an average score of 6.5/10 SMA III (grade XII) with an average score of 5.5/10</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Malaysia</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">SPM - Pass (D or higher) in 5 subjects <br>UEC - Overall pass (C8) average in 5 subjects, or<br>UEC Senior Middle 2 overall pass (C7) from the best 5 academic subjects, exclude Chinese and Malay<br>STPM - 5.0</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Myanmar</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Basic Education High School Examination (Matriculation Examination): overall score of at least 60% </td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Nepal</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Higher Secondary Certificate average of 55% OR <br>Proficiency/Intermediate Certificate average of 55</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Philippines</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">High School Diploma 80% (overall average of academic subjects only)</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Singapore</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">GCE O Levels - Pass in 5 academic subjects (minimum D grade) <br>GCE A Levels - Pass in 2 subjects (H2 level)</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Sri Lanka</td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Sri Lankan O Levels: ❛C❛ grade in 2 academic subjects and ❛S❛ grade in 3 academic subjects<br>Sri Lankan A Levels: ❛S❛ grade in 3 academic subjects </td></tr> <tr><td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Vietnam </td> <td colspan="1" style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-image: none">Successful completion of Year 11 with GPA 6.0/10</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br/><p></p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Special entry program</p> <p>If you are from a disadvantaged or underrepresented social, economic or cultural background, you may be eligible for one of our special admission programs. These programs are designed to help you access education more easily.</p> <p><a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/how-to-apply/special-admission-programs" href="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/how-to-apply/special-admission-programs" theme="primary"><span class="vu-link__inner"><!-- --><span>Learn more about special admission programs</span><!-- --><!-- --></span></a></p></div></div> <!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-collapsible-section__footer-text"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p></p></div></div></div></div></div> <div class="vu-courses--section--footer-text"><!-- --></div></div></div><div class="vu--additional-data item-type--collapsible_section"><!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="collapsible-sections-container vu-courses--additional-data--collapsible_section"><div class="vu-collapsible-section"><div class="vu-collapsible-section-title" tabindex="0"><!-- --> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Credit &amp; Entry pathways into this course</p> <div class="vu-collapsible-toggle-icon"> <!-- --></div></div> <div class="vu-collapsible-section-content--parent" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-collapsible-section-content"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"></div></div> <div class="vu-courses--additional-data--collapsible_section--accordion-list"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-courses--additional-data--collapsible_section--accordion-list--items"><div class="vu-accordion-wrapper"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-accordion__toggle-all"><button aria-label="" class="vu-button vu-button--tertiary vu-button--theme-light vu-button--size-small" data-v-6e5b367e=""> Open all </button></div> <dl class="vu-accordion vu-accordion--primary"><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-4" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Pathways at VU </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-4" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p></p> <p>If you don❛t currently have the English, maths, or other skills needed to complete this course, our <a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/courses/vce-preparation-english-language" href="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/courses/vce-preparation-english-language" theme="primary"><span class="vu-link__inner"><!-- --><span>English and Preparation courses</span><!-- --><!-- --></span></a> may help you transition into tertiary learning.</p></div></div> <div class="vu-grid-container vu-card-link__grid-container vu-card-link__grid-container--grey-extra-light no-gutter-rl"><div class="vu-grid-container__inner"></div></div> <br/></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-5" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Recognition of Prior Learning </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-5" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>You may be able to complete your qualification sooner through formal recognition of your existing skills. This is known as <a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/courses/credit-for-skills-past-study/recognition-of-prior-learning-rpl" href="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/courses/credit-for-skills-past-study/recognition-of-prior-learning-rpl" theme="primary"><span class="vu-link__inner"><!-- --><span>Recognition of Prior Learning (RPL).</span><!-- --><!-- --></span></a></p> <p>To receive RPL, we assess your previous work, education and life experiences against recognised qualifications. Applications for RPL can be made prior to enrolling.</p> <p>Call us on 1300 TAFE VP (1300 823 3