class="vu-card-link__left"><div class="h5"><span class="prepend" style="display:none;"> </span>Diploma of Golf Management </div> <div class="vu-card-link-details"><span>PGA International Golf Institute, Australia | 96 credit points</span></div></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vu-grid-cell--12 vu-grid-cell--12@l-up vu-grid-cell--6@xl-up"><div class="vu-card-link vu-card-link__primary"><div class="no-card-link"><div class="vu-card-link__main"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-card-link__left"><div class="h5"><span class="prepend" style="display:none;"> </span>Diploma of Sport </div> <div class="vu-card-link-details"><span>SEDA Group, Australia | 96 credit points</span></div></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vu-grid-cell--12 vu-grid-cell--12@l-up vu-grid-cell--6@xl-up"><div class="vu-card-link vu-card-link__primary"><div class="no-card-link"><div class="vu-card-link__main"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-card-link__left"><div class="h5"><span class="prepend" style="display:none;"> </span>Diploma of Sport </div> <div class="vu-card-link-details"><span>SEDA Group, Australia | 96 credit points</span></div></div> <div class="vu-card-link__right"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> <br/></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-12" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Credit for skills &amp; past study </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-12" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>If you have completed study with another university or institution you may be eligible to receive <a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/courses/credit-for-skills-past-study" href="https