UPDATE courses SET
    course_description = '<div class="vu-box-container__inner anchor-boxes vu-box-container__primary vu-container no-gutter-rl overview" data-id="overview" data-title="Overview" id="overview"><div class="vu-container"><p style="font-weight: bold;">Overview</p> <div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p class="paragraph--lead">Gain highly valued skills to combat hackers and digital scammers by studying for the Diploma of Cyber Security at Victoria University.</p></div></div> <!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu--additional-data item-type--basic-text"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-courses--additional-data--basic-text vu-courses--additional-data--basic-text--white"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>As cyber threats continue to evolve, businesses and governments urgently need skilled professionals to safeguard their data and systems. With a significant shortage of qualified individuals, now is the ideal time to start your career in cybersecurity. </p><p>A Diploma in Cyber Security provides the foundational skills and knowledge required to identify, prevent, and respond to cyber threats. You❛ll be well-prepared to enter the workforce, having gained hands-on experience with cutting-edge security technologies and practices, including:</p><ul><li>ethical hacking</li><li>digital forensics</li><li>network security</li><li>threat analysis</li><li>vulnerability assessment</li><li>incident response. </li></ul><p>You will graduate with theoretical and technical knowledge and skills to advance your career opportunities. Whether you❛re a recent graduate or considering a career change, this qualification is your gateway to secure, entry-level positions in an industry essential to the modern world.</p><p>If you complete this diploma, you will be eligible for a guaranteed place in the second year of the Bachelor of Cyber Security at Victoria University.</p></div></div> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --></div><div class="vu--additional-data item-type--accordion-list"><!-- --> <div class="vu-courses--additional-data--accordion-list"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu--additional-data--accordion-list--items"><div class="vu-accordion-wrapper"><!-- --> <!-- --> <div class="vu-accordion__toggle-all"><button aria-label="" class="vu-button vu-button--tertiary vu-button--theme-light vu-button--size-small" data-v-6e5b367e=""> Open all </button></div> <dl class="vu-accordion vu-accordion--primary"><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-4" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Learning outcomes </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-4" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>On successful completion of this course, students will be able to:</p> <ol><li>Demonstrate a broad understanding of fundamental information technology concepts in key areas such as network security, operating systems, ethical hacking, and incident response.</li> <li>Employ the latest technologies and develop self-learning abilities to address and solve real-world cybersecurity challenges.</li> <li>Exhibit a range of interpersonal and academic skills with a strong emphasis on practical development, both independently and in collaborative environments.</li> <li>Demonstrate the ability to engage in cybersecurity practice, independently or collaboratively, with a strong industry focus while taking responsibility for lifelong learning and professional growth.</li></ol></div></div></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-5" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Be part of a growing industry </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-5" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>With more and more companies adopting cloud services and storage, valuable data and information systems are increasingly under threat from hackers and industrial spies.</p><p>Beyond just accessing information, hackers can penetrate enterprise networks, encrypt the hard drive of computers and extort the organisation or computer owners to pay for unlocking the system.</p><p>Globally, cyber security is expected to have an annual growth of over 20% in the next five years.</p></div></div></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-6" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Study in workshop-style classes instead of lectures </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-6" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>Study this course via our award-winning VU Block Model®, where you complete one subject at a time over four weeks, rather than juggling several at once. </p><p>Learning in workshop-style classes, you’ll develop strong connections with your peers and practical skills for your future career. </p><p>You’ll also get fast feedback on your assignments, helping you to improve quickly as you progress through your course.</p><p><a class="vu-link vu-text-link" data-print-url="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/why-choose-vu/vu-block-model" href="https://www.vu.edu.au/study-at-vu/why-choose-vu/vu-block-model" theme="primary"><span class="vu-link__inner"><!-- --><span>Learn more about the VU Block Model®</span><!-- --><!-- --></span></a> </p></div></div></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-7" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Get the latest industry knowledge </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-7" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>Our experienced academic staff have a strong track record in cyber security research, providing you with a modern, up-to-date course.</p><p>The course has been designed in collaboration with experts in the cyber security industry to ensure you have insights into the latest developments in this field.</p></div></div></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-8" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Graduate ready for work through practical experience </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-8" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>To prepare you for professional challenges, we have created a simulated work environment where you will learn to assess risk and control cyber-security threats.</p><p>You will be given real-world problems to solve, as sourced from industry. With a hands-on approach to cyber security, you will gain expertise in network security, ethical hacking, and incident detection and response. </p><p>Through these practical experiences, you will develop the ability to assess, manage, and mitigate cyber-security threats, and graduate ready for a successful career in the field.</p></div></div></dd></div><div class="vu-accordion__item"><dt class="vu-accordion__title"><!-- --> <button aria-controls="vu-accordion-9" aria-expanded="false" class="vu-accordion__button"> <span class="vu-accordion__button-text"> Benefit from hybrid learning </span></button></dt> <dd class="vu-accordion__content" id="vu-accordion-9" style="display:none;"><div class="vu-markup tide-wysiwyg app-wysiwyg vu-accordion__content-inner"><!-- --> <div class="vu-markup__inner"><p>Our Diploma of Cyber Security follows a hybrid learning model and is delivered through a combination of on-campus (in-person) classes 2 days a week and online classes 1 day per week.</p><p>You❛ll be able to access resources and complete activities online, prior to attending face-to-face sessions, where your learning will be consolidated.</p></div></div></dd></div></dl></div></div></div> <!-- --> <!-- --> <!-- --></div></div></div>',
    total_course_duration = '1 year full time or longer for part time',
